summary: The module defines a dataclass that aggregates all configurable parameters for the ONNX Runtime backend used in the benchmarking suite. It includes options for selecting execution providers, device allocation, quantization and calibration settings, as well ...
business_intent: Provide a structured way to configure the ONNX Runtime backend for benchmarking, ensuring users can easily specify and manage settings related to execution providers, devices, quantization, and calibration.
